        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Legal Solutions</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          AI-powered legal practice management and client communication services for law firms of all sizes
        </p>
      </div>

